    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced garlic </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until golden</p><p>Tip: Watch the garlic like a hawk to make sure it doesn't burn!</p><p>Once golden, transfer the<strong> garlic</strong> to kitchen paper, set aside and reserve the pan for later – this is your<strong> pan-fried garlic</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice the <strong>spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
